desc: At Ballstad we know what it takes to make a high quality Omega-3 and Collagen supplement, giving you the best of what Norway has to offer.

layout.text: In Norway, Omega-3 rich fish oils has always been a natural part of a healthy diet, strengthening body and mind, so that Norwegians can live long and healthy lives. With Ballstad fresh Omega-3, we now bring the secret to the world.
